        Builder of the class SIA It carries out a local copy of the name of the files for their posterior use
        Then, obtains the data from the input files and stores it in a structure for the program
        Finally, it creates the possible bounds for the attribute values
        Parameters:
        ftrain - Name of the input training data-set
        feval - Name of the input validation data-set
        ftest - Name of the input test data-set
        fSalidatr - Name of the output training data-set
        fSalidatst - Name of the output test data-set
        fsal - Name of the oupput statistics file
        seed - seed for the random generator
        nb - Maximum number of iterations of the genetic algorithm
        alfa - parameter for the criterium of the rule evaluation
        beta - parameter for the criterium of the rule evaluation
        Tstr - Threshold for the rule filtering
